snippet: Southeastern Asset management says that proposals from the Blackstone Group and Carl C. Icahn are superior to the $13.65-a-share offer from Michael S. Dell and the private equity firm Silver Lake.
abstract: Southeastern Asset management says that proposals from the Blackstone Group and Carl C. Icahn are superior to the $13.65-a-share offer from Michael S. Dell and the private equity firm Silver Lake.

headline.main: Big Dell Shareholder Prefers 2 Rival Bids
